name: Mark Timothy Agarrado
text: Lol i tried one - I didn’t even make it past the registration page.     They gave options to provide FB or number, i chose to register via number, but it sent an error message to register using FB instead.    Didn’t continue after that, haha. Ang kadiri parang project ng college student, hahahaha.
